00:55:51,016 --> 00:55:52,416
Ayah.

342
00:55:53,483 --> 00:55:54,983
Sayang, tolong berhenti.

343
00:55:57,460 --> 00:55:58,800
Puan,

344
00:55:59,021 --> 00:56:00,821
awak tidak perlu buat begitu.

345
00:56:01,216 --> 00:56:02,616
Jangan...

346
00:56:03,201 --> 00:56:04,801
masuk campur.

347
00:56:06,595 --> 00:56:08,865
Apa? Tidak guna.

348
00:56:09,073 --> 00:56:10,273
Tidak guna...

349
00:56:14,820 --> 00:56:17,790
Baiklah,
mari kita selesaikan hal ini.

